snippet.title: BADBLOOD - TREAD LIGHTLY
snippet.description:
"WHAT KEEPS MANKIND ALIVE?"

BADBLOOD is now available to play on Steam and itch.io!:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com//app/404400
Itch.io: http://wsong.itch.io/badblood

http://wsong.me/badblood
http://twitter.com/songfeuds

BADBLOOD is a local split-screen hide & seek between two players, with a deadly consequence.

Music by Utopia, Ohio - Dogtooth North Dakota (http://freemusicarchive.org/music/Utopia_Ohio/Utopia_Ohio_and_other_Ghost_Towns/Utopia_Ohio_-_Utopia_Ohio_and_other_Ghost_Towns_-_02_Dogtooth_North_Dakota)
